meanings.definition: of the same kind; similar; homogeneous
meanings.english_definition: of the same kind; similar; homogeneous

examples.sentence: Barang-barang sejenis dikumpulkan di rak ini.
examples.translation: Items of the same type are collected on this shelf.

etymology.value: Derived from the prefix 'se-' (one, same) and 'jenis' (kind, type).
